div.p: RANGER a fworn officer of a foreſt, appointed by the king’s letters patent ; whoſe buſineſs is to walk through his charge, to drive back the deer out of the purlieus, &c. and to preſent all treſpaſſes within his. juriſdiction at the next foreſt-court.
